## Backend-struktur (`backend/app/api/v1/endpoints/`)

Alle endepunkter er montert under `/api/v1/` prefix.

**Hoveddomener:**
- `/properties`, `/units`, `/contracts`, `/parties` - Core CRUD
- `/dashboard`, `/analytics` - Stats og oversikter
- `/risk`, `/deviations`, `/internal-control`, `/checklists` - HMS
- `/hms/activities` - Planlagte HMS-aktiviteter
- `/ai/chat`, `/agent/chat`, `/lab/chat` - AI-tjenester
- `/search/vector`, `/search/global` - Sû¡k
- `/admin/*` - Administrasjon
- `/external/*` - Eksterne APIer
- `/mcp/*` - MCP-tjenester
- `/cost-management/*`, `/financials/*` - ûkonomi
